stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> mode_default

    mode_default --> plan: /plan 或 EnterPlanModeTool
    plan --> mode_default: ExitPlanModeTool
    mode_default --> acceptEdits: --permission-mode acceptEdits
    mode_default --> bypassPermissions: --dangerously-skip-permissions
    acceptEdits --> mode_default: 重置
    plan --> plan: 转移副作用清除 needsPlanModeExitAttachment

    note right of plan
        进入：清除 exit attachment
        离开：设置 exit attachment
    end note

    note right of bypassPermissions
        bubble 只在子 Agent 内部使用
        auto 仅内部构建可见
    end note
